# Frontend build-time configuration for Book Haven.
#
# In Replit (dev or production deployment) you do NOT need this file —
# the frontend and API are served on the same origin via the workspace
# reverse-proxy and `/api/...` resolves automatically.
#
# When deploying the frontend to GitHub Pages and the API to Railway
# (or any other host), set VITE_API_URL to the public origin of your
# Railway API. Do NOT include a trailing slash and do NOT include `/api`.
#
# Example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://book-haven-api.up.railway.app
VITE_API_URL=
